<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.7.10">
<l>ceṅka ṇāḷi yiṭṭiṟaiñcuñ ciṅkavēḷ kuṉṟuṭaiya</l>
<l>eṅka ḷīca ṉempirāṉai yiruntamiḻ nūṟpulavaṉ</l>
<l>maṅkai yāḷaṉ maṉṉutolcīr vaṇṭaṟai tārkkaliyaṉ</l>
<l>ceṅkai yāḷaṉ ceñcolmālai vallavart tītilarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master this garland of fine words of him of eternal ancient fame,</l>
<l>Ruler of Maṅkai, the one with a fine [liberal] hand, scholar of vast Tamil texts,</l>
<l>Of Kaliyaṉ, with a garland where bees hum, about our god</l>
<l rend="indent">of Lion-Man Mountain,</l>
<l>Where lions with glowing eyes bow and place [offerings],</l>
<l rend="indent">they will be without fault.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
